                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the GRAMERCY IS EM trademark.
                           






On Friday, June 24, 2011,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        GRAMERCY IS EM by 
                        Gramercy Funds Management LLC, Greenwich, CT  06830.
                        The USPTO has given the GRAMERCY IS EM 
                        trademark serial  number of  85355692.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is ABANDONED - FAILURE TO RESPOND OR LATE RESPONSE.
