July 28, 2017 8:32 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Gramercy Funds Management LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Gramercy Funds Management LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. It provides its services to pooled investment vehicles, pension plans, foundations, public retirement funds, endowments, high net worth investors, pooled investment funds, other investment advisors and corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It also manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe primarily in emerging countries. For its debt investments it employs long-only debt strategy. For its equity investments, the firm employs a long only equity strategy. For its alternative investments, it invests in...
Gramercy Funds Management LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. It provides its services to pooled investment vehicles, pension plans, foundations, public retirement funds, endowments, high net worth investors, pooled investment funds, other investment advisors and corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It also manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe primarily in emerging countries. For its debt investments it employs long-only debt strategy. For its equity investments, the firm employs a long only equity strategy. For its alternative investments, it invests in emerging markets distressed debt and special situations. The firm employs fundamental analysis along with bottom-up stock picking approach to create its portfolios. Gramercy Funds Management LLC was founded in 1998 and is based in Greenwich, Connecticut with offices in London, United Kingdom; Hong Kong; Singapore; Mexico City, Mexico and Silicon Valley, California.
Detailed Description


